msgid "Eventos, webhooks y jobs programados"
msgstr "Events, webhooks and scheduled jobs"

msgid "Tu API de eventos en un solo lugar"
msgstr "Your events API in one place"

msgid "Publica eventos con cualquier payload, configura webhooks con filtros y recibe POST en tiempo real. Programa tareas recurrentes (diario, semanal, mensual o cron) que emitan eventos o llamen a tus URLs. Todo con una API simple y un token."
msgstr "Publish events with any payload, configure webhooks with filters and receive POST in real time. Schedule recurring tasks (daily, weekly, monthly or cron) that emit events or POST to your URLs. All with a simple API and one token."

msgid "Crear cuenta gratis"
msgstr "Create free account"

msgid "Ya tengo cuenta"
msgstr "I already have an account"

msgid "Qué puedes hacer"
msgstr "What you can do"

msgid "Una sola API, un token, y control total sobre eventos, entregas y tareas programadas."
msgstr "One API, one token, and full control over events, deliveries and scheduled tasks."

msgid "Eventos"
msgstr "Events"

msgid "Publica eventos con topic y payload JSON vía API. Sin esquemas fijos: envía lo que necesites y nosotros lo enrutamos."
msgstr "Publish events with topic and JSON payload via API. No fixed schemas: send what you need and we route it."

msgid "Webhooks"
msgstr "Webhooks"

msgid "Configura URLs de destino, filtros por topic o por campos del payload, y recibe POST en tiempo real. Reintentos automáticos y seguimiento de entregas."
msgstr "Configure destination URLs, filters by topic or payload fields, and receive POST in real time. Automatic retries and delivery tracking."

msgid "Jobs programados"
msgstr "Scheduled jobs"

msgid "Tareas recurrentes: diario, semanal, mensual o cron. Cada ejecución puede emitir un evento o hacer POST a una URL con el payload que definas."
msgstr "Recurring tasks: daily, weekly, monthly or cron. Each run can emit an event or POST to a URL with the payload you define."

msgid "API Key"
msgstr "API Key"

msgid "Un solo token para toda la API: eventos, webhooks, jobs y más. Genera y regenera desde el dashboard. Bearer o X-Api-Key."
msgstr "One token for the whole API: events, webhooks, jobs and more. Generate and regenerate from the dashboard. Bearer or X-Api-Key."

msgid "¿Listo para empezar?"
msgstr "Ready to get started?"

msgid "Regístrate gratis. Sin tarjeta. Crea tu proyecto, obtén tu token y empieza a enviar eventos en minutos."
msgstr "Sign up for free. No card required. Create your project, get your token and start sending events in minutes."

